        "869": {
          "vnum": 869,
          "name": "Inside the Mouth",
          "description": "Rough, porous rock makes up the surface of the cave. The jagged, almost carved floor of the place makes travel difficult. Oddly formed stalactites litter the ceiling, but you see no evidence of the water that created them.",
