        "870": {
          "vnum": 870,
          "name": "Cave Fork",
          "description": "At this point the cave no longer tries to follow along one route. Paths break off and move through the rock at what looks to be roughly west, east and southeast. Covering the entire southwestern wall is some sort of primitive mural.",
