        "785": {
          "vnum": 785,
          "name": "In the Swamp",
          "description": "Your feet squish deep into the mossy muck that becomes an unnavigable wasteland anywhere except north. A rickety gate lies between you and a cottage provides an arched bridge over the quickmud to your southeast.",
