          "vnum": 790,
          "name": "Side of the House",
          "description": "Tall dead weeds engulf the side of the house and possibly a fence to the east -- as you've tried and failed to push further through that way. Noises can be heard from inside the house through the weeds on your left. Southwest takes you back around toward the front of the house, and south, sends you back towards the swamp.",
